    "##### Ratings appear inconsistent in some entries.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Programmatic Assessment\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Using methods such as .info(), .isnull().sum(), .duplicated().sum(), and .describe(), several quality and tidiness issues were identified.\n",
